    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Notice: Original Game was not designed to have DLCs, and it remains that way. No extra contents are added via DLC.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, this DLC exists to quick-unlocks some stuff that can be unlocked by just playing in the game. <i>This is a feature asked by some players that wanted to play with all characters and some specific filters right from start.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Slam and Roll - Freedom DLC contains unlocks:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- All game areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock all visual filters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock all characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock all game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also adds 5 additional credits from the base game to be used in arcade modes.</p>",
